Obulwadde bwa kolonavirusi (COVID-19) mu Union/Ekifo kya Bulaaya eky'Eby'enfuna ne mu Bungereza okuva nga January 1 okutuuka nga March 15, 2020
Obukadde bw'abalwadde ba coronavirus (COVID-19) bulaga enkola y'emu mu mawanga g'ekibiina kya European Union/European Economic Area ne mu Bungereza, nga bukakasa nti wadde nga buli ggwanga liri mu mbeera ya njawulo, ekirwadde kya COVID-19 kikulaakulana mu nsi zonna.
Okusinziira ku by'obudde mu Italy, amawanga, amalwaliro n'ebifo eby'obujjanjabi birina okwetegekera obulungi ekirwadde kya COVID-19 ekijja okwetaaga okulabirirwa n'okusingira ddala okujjanjabibwa ennyo.
Nga December 31, 2019, ekitundu ky'abalwadde b'obulwadde bw'ensusu obutasobose kyalagibwa mu Wuhan, Hubei Province, China.
Nga January 9, 2020, ekitongole kya China eky'okwerinda endwadde ne kitegeeza nti ekirwadde kino kye kivudde mu coronavirus empya, kati eyitibwa SARS-CoV-2.
Okuva olwo, obulwadde obuva ku SARS-CoV-2 buyitibwa obulwadde bwa coronavirus (COVID-19).
Obujulizi obutuuse wano nti abantu 80 ku buli kikumi abalina COVID-19 bafuna obulwadde obutali bwa maanyi, kwe kugamba, obulwadde bw'omu myoyo obulimu oba obutalimu pulmonary disease, era abasinga obungi ku bo bawona.
Mu bitundu ebitundu 14 ku buli kikumi, COVID-19 yeeyongerayo ddala okuba ey'amaanyi nga yeetaaga okudda mu ddwaliro, ate mu bitundu ebitundu 6 ku buli kikumi, yeeyongerayo ddala okuba ey'amaanyi nga yeetaaga obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi.
Okufa kw'abalwadde abali mu malwaliro olw'ekirwadde kya COVID-19 kuli 4%.
Mu kunoonyereza kuno, twekenneenyezza enkulaakulana y'obubenje bwa COVID-19 mu buli ggwanga lya Bulaaya/Ekifo ky'Eby'enfuna ekya Bulaaya (EU/EEA) ne mu Bungereza era ne tugeraageranya n'ebyo ebiri mu ssaza lya Hubei mu China.
Twageraageranya n'omuwendo gw'abantu abaakafuna COVID-19 mu nsi za EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza ne Italy wakati wa January 31 ne March 15, 2020.
Embeera za COVID-19 mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza
Oluvannyuma lwa China, COVID-19 yeeyongedde okubuna mu nsi yonna, era ebikolwa by'obulwadde bwa COVID-19 mu nsi yonna kati bigoberera ebya China.
Nga March 11, 2020, director general w'ekitongole ky'ensi yonna eky'ebyobulamu (WHO) yalangirira COVID-19 ng'ekirwadde ekirwadde ekikambwe.
Olupapula lwa March 5 olwa Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. baalaze nga waliwo abantu abaasooka okukakasibwa nti balina COVID-19 mu Bulaaya, okusinziira ku ntegeka y'ekirwadde eya WHO.
Mu EU/EEA, abantu basatu abaasoose okukakasibwa baategeezebwa okuva e Bufalansa nga 24 January 2020 nga bava e Wuhan mu Hubei Province, China.
Nga 15 March 2020, abantu ba COVID-19 baali bamaze okuzuulibwa mu nsi 30 ez'omu EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza, era wakati wa 31 December 2019 ne ku lunaku olwayogeddwako waggulu, abantu 39,768 be baali bakwatiddwa ne 1,727 be baafa, nga 17,750 be baali bakwatiddwa ne 1,441 be baafa mu Italy yokka.
Okufuna omuwendo gw'abantu abaakafa n'obubonero bw'abantu abaakafa
Mu kitongole kya Bulaaya eky'okutangira n'okulabirira endwadde (ECDC), omuwendo gw'abantu abaakabuulirwa ku COVID-19 mu buli ggwanga mu nsi yonna, nga guva mu bitabo bya gavumenti byokka, gamba nga Minisitule y'ebyobulamu mu nsi, ab'obuyinza mu by'obulamu mu ggwanga ne mu bitundu, ne mu kitongole kya WHO, gukuzibwa buli lunaku ku ssaawa 8:00.
Ebyavudde mu kunoonyereza kuno bikozesebwa okwetegereza embeera za COVID-19 mu EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza, n'okugeraageranya ku Italy.
Ng'okulowooza ku muwendo gw'abantu abalina COVID-19 nga bakyali mu bulamu, tubalirira ennaku 14 ez'abantu abalina COVID-19, nga bwe kiri mu buli ggwanga lya EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza wakati wa January 1 ne March 15, 2020.
Era tulaze omuwendo gw'abantu abaabadde bakubiddwa mu buli ggwanga nga 15 March 2020 ku ssaawa 8:00 ez'ekiro, era nga tugeraageranya ku Italy okuva ku 31 January okutuuka ku 15 March 2020.
Enkulaakulana ya COVID-19 mu nsi za EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza
Enkola y'ennaku 14 ez'omuggalo ogw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza mu bujjuvu, yakwatagana n'ey'omu Hubei Province mu China (Ekifaananyi 1).
Mu bujjuvu, eri EU/EEA ne Bungereza, omuwendo gw'abantu abaakafa COVID-19 gwatandika okwetoloola nga 21 Febwali ne gukula nnyo nga 28 Febwali 2020 (okunyweza).
Kino kyava ku kwongera kw'abatuuze mu Italy, naye amawanga gonna aga EU/EEA ne Bungereza galaga enkulaakulana y'omuwendo gw'abantu abaakafuna COVID-19 (okunyweza).
Ekifaananyi 2 kiraga omuwendo gw'abantu abaakafuna COVID-19 mu nsi za EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza nga bageraageranyizibwa ku Italy okuva nga January 31 okutuuka nga March 15, 2020.
Ekiraga nti nga 15 March ku ssaawa 8 ez'ekiro, amawanga 15 amalala mu EU/EEA ne Bungereza gaali gaakawandiika omuwendo gw'abalwadde ogugeraageranyizibwa ku gwa Italy wiiki 3 emabega oba nga tezinnaba.
Ebivudde mu kunoonyereza kwaffe biraga nti omuwendo gw'abantu abaalabikiddwa nga balina COVID-19 gweyongedde nnyo mu EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza.
Enkola eziri mu kuddamu okusaasaana kw'ekirwadde kya COVID-19 ziraga nti ekirwadde kino kikulaakulana mu ngeri y'emu mu nsi zonna.
Kino kibaawo wadde nga ensi ziri mu mitendera egy'enjawulo, enjawulo mu nkola z'obujjanjabi mu mawanga, era nga wayinza okubaawo enjawulo mu ngeri gye bategeeramu abalwadde mu mawanga, n'enkola ez'enjawulo ez'okulonda abalwadde abajja okukeberebwa okukakasa COVID-19, omuli n'okwekebejja okw'okuddaabiriza.
Mu ntandikwa ya March 2020, abasawo mu bitundu bya Italy ebikwatiddwako ekirwadde kino baalaze embeera nga abalwadde 10 ku buli kikumi abalina COVID-19 beetaaga obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi, era emikutu gy'empuliziganya gyagamba nti amalwaliro ne ebitongole ebikuuma obulwadde obw'amaanyi mu bitundu ebyo byali bituuse ku bukulu bwabyo.
Ebikwata ku kusibibwa mu ddwaliro ne/oba mu kitanda kya COVID-19 bibeerawo mu EU/EEA ku mutindo gwa 6% ne 1% byokka (ebiri mu katabo)
Kyokka, birina okukuÅÅaanyizibwa mu ngeri entegeke obulungi okusobola okwongera ku by'okwetegereza ebiriwo nga byesigamye ku muwendo gw'abantu abaakabuulirwa n'omuwendo gw'abantu abaafa.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa wakati wa 2010 ne 2011 kwalaga enjawulo ey'amaanyi mu bbeeyi z'ekitanda ekya IUD n'ekirala ekya semi-intensive unit mu Bulaaya, okuva ku bitanda 29,2 mu Bugirimaani okutuuka ku bitanda 4,2 mu Portugal buli bantu 100,000.
Kino kitegeeza nti ensi ziyinza okuba n'ensimbi ezisinga oba ezisingawo ku za Italy (12.5 ez'ebitanda bya IUD n'ebisambi eby'amaanyi mu 2010-2011 ku bantu 100,000).
Ebika eby'enkola ebikwatagana n'okutuuka ku buyinza mu by'obujjanjabi, nga mu buli ggwanga lya EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza, obwenkanankana bw'abatuuze abajjanjabibwa mu malwaliro olw'ekirwadde kya COVID-19 nga balina akabi akali ku bitundu 90 ku buli 100 mu busobozi bw'ebitanda ebirimu obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi, biweereddwa mu kuddamu okw'omukaaga okw'ekigezo eky'obutebenkevu ekya ECDC ekikwata ku COVID-19.
Olw'okuba okutuusa kati, abantu bangi nnyo bali mu bitundu bya EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza, era ng'amalwaliro n'ebizimbe eby'obuyambi obw'amaanyi bijjanjaba abantu ab'enjawulo, obubaka obukwata ku bantu n'ebitanda eby'obuyambi obw'amaanyi bulina okuweebwayo mu nnamba ya Nomenclature of Territorial Units for Statistical Purposes 2 (NUTS-2).
Ekyokulabirako kya Italy n'enkulaakulana mu mawanga amalala biraga nti ekirwadde kya COVID-19 kikulaakulana mu bwangu mu EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza.
Ensi, amalwaliro n'ebifo eby'obutebenkevu bikyetaaga okwetegekera embeera y'okusasaanya SARS-CoV-2 mu bantu n'okweyongera kw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 abetaaga obujjanjabi, naddala obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi, nga bwe kiri mu bitundu bya Italy ebikwatiddwako ekirwadde kino.
Nga bwe kyalagibwa mu kunoonyereza ku kabi akali mu bbanga ery'ebbanga, ekidduka ekyangu, ekyeggulawo era ekyenjawulo kikulu nnyo mu kulwisa okusaasaana kwa SARS-CoV-2, nga kikyuse okuva ku ngeri y'okukugira okutuuka ku ngeri y'okukendeezaamu, kubanga okwongera kw'abalwadde okw'amaanyi ennyo kuyinza obuteebereza bannannyini kusalawo n'amalwaliro nga balina ekiseera ekimala okutegeera, okukkiriza n'okukyusa ebikolwa byabwe singa tebabikolerawo mu bwangu.
Okulowooza ku kabi akali mu bwangu era kulaga obulwadde bw'abantu obunaagonjoolwa.
Waliwo akaseera akatono amawanga mwe gasobola okwongera ku mitendera gy'okukugira SARS-CoV-2 okukendeera n'okuggyawo ebizibu mu by'obulamu.
Singa enteekateeka zino zilemererwa, enkola z'ebyobulamu mu mawanga amalala mu EU/EEA ziyinza okubaamu obulwadde obw'amaanyi mu nnaku oba wiiki ezijja.
Ekirwadde kya coronavirus ekya 2019 (COVID-19), ekireeteddwa obulwadde bwa coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) obw'ekikangabwa ekinene (SARS), kimaze okutta abantu abasukka mu 3,000 n'okukosa abalala abasukka mu 80,000 mu China ne mu nsi yonna, nga kiviiriddeko abantu okubonaabona.
Okufaananako akawuka ak'omugenzi, SARS-CoV, akaaleetera abantu enkumi n'enkumi okufuna SARS mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 nayo esobola okuyitibwa okuva mu biwuka ebikambwe era ne kireeta obubonero obufaananako ng'obwo.
Kyokka, COVID-19 si ya maanyi nnyo era tefa nnyo okusinga SARS, naye esobola okutaasa abantu bangi, era ekwata nnyo ku bantu abakaddiye okusinga ku bato, era esinga okukwata ku basajja okusinga ku bakazi.
Ng'eddamu ku kwongera kw'ebitabo ebikwatagana n'obulwadde obupya, ekitundu kino kigenda kulaga engeri gye bukwataganamu n'obuyigirize obwa bulijjo.
Tujja kwekenneenya emisingi egy'obutondebwanga, obwabantu, obwa virology, okunoonyereza, okujjanjaba, okusoomoozebwa n'okutangira obulwadde.
Wadde ng'ebibuuzo bingi bikyali byetaaga eby'okuddamu, tusuubira nti okunoonyereza kuno kujja kuyamba mu kutegeera n'okumalawo obulwadde buno obw'akabi.
Embaga y'omwaka ogwayita nga January 25, 2020 yafuuka ekijjukizo eky'enjawulo era ekitayinza kwerabirwa eri Abakiina bonna abawalirizibwa okubeera mu kkomera mu luwummula lwonna n'ebiseera ebirala bingi olw'ekirwadde ekirala ekyavaako akawuka.
Akawuka kano kayisa nnyo aka coronavirus (CoV) akaaleetawo ekirwadde kya SSARS mu 2003; n'olwekyo, World Health Organization (WHO) yakayita SARS-CoV-2 nga February 11, 2020, era obulwadde obwalina erinnya CoV-19 (COVID-19).
Ekirwadde kino kyatandika mu Wuhan, China, ne kibula mu ggwanga lyonna ne mu nsi endala nga 50 okwetooloola ensi.
Nga Maaki 2, 2020, akawuka kano kaali kavuddemu abantu abasukka 80,000 abaakazuulibwa nga balina COVID-19, nga n'abalwadde abasukka 40,000 bawonyezebwa era n'abalwadde abasukka 3,000 ne bafa.
WHO erabula nti COVID-19 ye "mulabe wa bantu ow'omutindo ogusooka", era ayinza okuba ow'amaanyi okusinga obutujju.
Okusinziira ku PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), mu bbanga eritawera myezi ebiri, ebitundu ebisukka mu 200 bifulumiziddwa ku COVID-19, omuli obuwuka, obulwadde, obulwadde, okunoonyereza n'obujjanjabi, okuva ku lipoota esooka eya Jjanwali 7, 2020, eyasalawo ku ngeri gye yalagamu akawuka akaali kaggiddwawo okuva mu balwadde abangi.
Ekitundu kino kigenda kulaga engeri okunoonyereza gye kugenda mu kitundu kino ekiggya ekikulira mu bwangu.
Nga bwe kiba kyetaagisa, tujja kugeraageranya COVID-19 ku SARS n'obulwadde obulala obuleetebwa CoV, Middle East Respiratory Syndrome (MERS, ekirwadde kya 2012).
Era tujja kwogera ku bye tuyize ku bulwadde buno n'engeri gye buyinza okutangirwamu n'ebizibu ebirala ebikulu.
CoVs zitwalibwa ng'ebirwadde ebitafiirayo abantu, nga zikola kumpi 15% ku bulwadde bw'ekibira.
Kyokka, mu kyasa kino, tulabye emirundi ebiri nti waliwo obuwuka obuyitibwa SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV, obwaviirako ekirwadde ekyatandika mu China mu 2003 ne Saudi Arabia mu 2012, era oluvannyuma ne bujja mu nsi endala ezitali zimu nga bulwadde n'okufa bicaase nnyo.
N'olwekyo, COVID-19 eya kaakano ye CoV ey'okusatu mu byafaayo by'omuntu.
Nga bwe kiragibwa mu Fig. Fig.1,1, ekitundu ky'obulwadde bwa mmotoka obuli mu bifo ebitamanyiddwa kyasooka kutegeezebwa mu Wuhan nga December 31, 2019 mu kakiiko k'ebyobulamu aka China.
Nga wayise ennaku musanvu, ekirwadde kya CoV kyayisibwa.
Nga January 15, 2020, omusango gw'okufa ogwasooka mu Wuhan gwatuusibwa.
Mu kiseera kye kimu, ekirwadde kyagenda mu bibuga, amasaza, n'amawanga agali okumpi.
Nga January 20, obulwadde bw'abakozi ba ddwaliro bwabadde bukwatiddwa, nga kiraga nti abantu basobola okussa ekirwadde kino.
Nga January 23, ekibuga Wuhan kyaggalwawo, nga n'entambula ya bonna ekutte.
Nga January 24, okunoonyereza okwasooka ku bulwadde buno kwalaga nti ku balwadde 41 abaabadde bakakasibwa, 21 bokka be baaliko n'abantu ab'omu katale k'ebyennyanja e Wuhan, ekitegeeza nti ekifo ekyatandikamu obulwadde buno ky'ebisolo ebitaamanyiddwa.
Nga January 30, WHO yalangirira ekirwadde kino ng'embeera y'obutakyabaga mu nsi yonna.
Mu kiseera kino, obulwadde buno bubadde busasaana mu China n'amawanga amalala nga 50 mu nsi yonna (Ekifaananyi (Ekifaananyi.2).2).
Olw'embeera okwonooneka amangu, omuwendo n'obunene bw'ekirwadde kino bikyaliwo.
Nga February 11, 2020, okunoonyereza ku bifo ebyenjawulo okwaliwo abalwadde 8,866, omuli 4,021 abakakasizza nti balina COVID-19, kwalaga ekifaananyi ekisingako ku kya kiseera kino eky'ekirwadde kino nga bwe kiragibwa wammanga (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 ekutte abantu ab'emyaka gyonna, naddala abali wakati w'emyaka 30 ne 65.
Kumpi kimu kya kubiri (47.7%) ku abo abaakosebwa baali basukka mu myaka 50, abamu baali wansi wa myaka 20, era 14 bokka be baasoberwa baali wansi w'emyaka 10.
SARS-CoV-2 yakosa abasajja bangi (0.31/100,000) okusinga abakyala (0.27/100,000).
COVID-19 yeeyongedde mu bibinja, naddala mu Hubei ne mu bitundu ebiriraanyewo.
COVID-19 yaweebwa ennaku 5 (2 okutuuka 9) okuzuulibwa okusinziira ku ndabika y'obubonero.
Ekiseera eky'omuggalo kyali ennaku 4.8 (3.0 - 7.2).
