Lymphopenia, obutaba na musaayi, n'omutindo gwa creatine kinase bye bimu ku bintu ebitera okulabika mu SARS mu kugezesebwa mu ddagala.
Obulwadde bwa alveolar obwabula, okulya ebitundu by'omubiri n'okweyongera kw'omuwendo gw'ebitundu by'omubiri nabyo birabikira mu balwadde ba SARS.
Abalwadde abali wakati wa 20 ne 30 ku buli kikumi mu kiseera ekimu beetaaga obujjanjabi obw'amaanyi n'obuyambi bw'omukka.
Ng'oggyeko obuwuka obw'omunda, ebitundu ebirala nga mu byo mulimu endwadde z'omunda, ebinywa, n'ensiri, nabyo bisobola okukosebwa mu mbeera zino ez'amaanyi, nga kino kitera kubaawo nga waliwo ekirungo kya cytokine ekiyinza okuviirako okufa, naddala mu balwadde abalina obulwadde obw'omubiri obutagwa lubege.
Virusi eno yasooka kukyera mu biopsy y'omufuba gwa muganda wa mulwadde zero eyali ava e Guangzhou ng'agenda e Hong Kong.
Okuva olwo, okufuba okw'amaanyi kwe kwakoleddwa okunoonyereza ku HCoV.
HCoV-NL63 yawulirwa okuva mu mwana wa myezi 7 mu Netherlands mu nkomerero ya 2004.
Kyatandikiddewo okukizuula nti akawuka kano kajjudde abaana abato, bannamukadde, n'abalwadde abalina obulwadde bw'okufuuyira.
