Mu bbaluwa eno, twaddamu okuddibwamu ku bulagirizi bwaffe era ne tubawa enkola y'okuzuula "omulwadde eyeekakasa" ne "omulwadde akakasibwa" okusinziira ku Mitindo gy'Okulondoola n'Okujjanjaba COVID-19 (enkyusa ey'omusanvu) eyafulumizibwa akakiiko k'ebyobulamu aka National Health Committee of the People's Republic of China.
Mu Ddesemba 2019, akawuka ka coronavirus aka 2019 (2019-nCoV) kaaleetera ekirwadde kino okubalukawo, kati kayitibwa coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19), era akawuka kano kayitibwa severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Nga March 11, 2020, WHO yatongoza COVID-19 ng'obulwadde obw'amaanyi.
Okusobola okulwanyisa ekirwadde kya SARS-CoV-2, ttiimu yaffe yatonda ekiragiro ekyangu ekyassibwa ku Intaneeti mu Military Medical Research nga February 6, 2020.
Efunye okwetegereza okw'amaanyi okuva lwe yassibwa mu katabo kano.
Kyokka, weetegereze nti COVID-19 kirwadde kipya. Okutegeera kwaffe n'okumanya kweyongedde okusinziira ku kunoonyereza okukoleddwa buli kiseera n'okugezesebwa mu nkola y'ekisawo; era olw'ensonga eyo, enkola z'okumanya n'okujjanjaba nazo zikyusibwa buli kiseera.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, Enkola y'Okulondoola n'Okujjanjaba COVID-19 eyafulumizibwa akakiiko k'ebyobulamu aka National Health Committee of the People's Republic of China (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/) wakati wa January 16, 2020 ne March 3, 2020 erina ebitundu musanvu nga ebimu bikyusiddwa.
Omukulembeze waffe kati afunye ekirowoozo okuva eri Zhou et al., eyawa ekirowoozo ekyangu eky'okusala okusinziira ku by'obumanyirivu bwe mu ddwaliro.
Omulimu guno gwongedde obujulizi obupya mu bukulembeze bwaffe era era guwa n'ebirala eby'omugaso ku bulwadde buno obw'ensi yonna.
Tukkiriziganya n'omulimu gwe bakola era ne tubalaga okusiima kwaffe.
Kyokka, omulimu gwabwe era gwetaaga okuddaabirizibwa okusinziira ku by'okunoonyereza ebipya ebikwata ku COVID-19 (ekigezo eky'omusanvu) n'okunoonyereza okwakolebwa gye buvuddeko awo.
Okusinziira ku kufulumizibwa okw'omusanvu (3 March 2020), okukakasa ekika ky'omusuubirwa kyetaagisa okugatta ekimu ku bintu ebirimu ebyafaayo by'obulwadde n'ebitundu bibiri eby'obulabe okusobola okukola okunoonyereza okw'omugaso oba kyetaagisa okutuukiriza ebitundu bisatu eby'obulabe singa tewali byafaayo bya bulwadde bitegeerekeka bulungi:
Ebyafaayo by'obulwadde: (1) ebyafaayo by'okutambula oba okubeera mu kibuga Wuhan n'ebitundu ebiriraanyewo oba mu bitundu ebirala mwe baalagibwa nga balina COVID-19 mu nnaku 14 ezaasembayo nga tebannaba kulaga bubonero; (2) ebyafaayo by'okukwatagana n'abantu abalina SARS-CoV-2 (nga balina nucleic acid); (3) ebyafaayo by'okukwatagana n'abalwadde abalina omusujja oba obubonero bw'okufuuyira okuva mu kibuga Wuhan n'ebitundu ebiriraanyewo oba mu bitundu ebirala mwe baalagibwa nga balina COVID-19 mu nnaku 14 ezaasembayo nga tebannaba kulaga bubonero; (4) ebyafaayo by'okukwatagana n'abantu abaalagibwa nga balina obulwadde (okusinga oba okwenkanankana n'abalwadde babiri abaalina omusujja n'obubonero bw'okufuuyira mu bbanga lya wiiki 2 mu bifo ebitonotono, gamba ng'awaka, ofiisi, aw'okusomera, n'ebirala).
Ebirabika mu ddwaaliro: (1) omusujja ne/oba obubonero bw'okufuuyira; (2) ng'olina ekirwadde kya COVID-19 ekiriko ebifaananyi; (3) omuwendo gw'omusaayi omweru nga gubaamu obubonero obuguddewo oba obugguddewo mu kiseera eky'okusookera ddala.
Okuzuulibwa kw'omulwadde akakasiddwa kulina kwesigama ku kuba nti waliwo ekikebeddwa mu bulwadde buno: (1) okwekebejjebwa ku SARS-CoV-2 nga kirina PCR; (2) okwekebejjebwa ku genome y'ekika ky'omusaayi nga kirina omuwendo omungi ku coronaviruses empya; (3) okukeberebwa ku SARS-CoV-2 nga kirina IgM ne IgG; oba okukeberebwa ku SARS-CoV-2 nga kirina IgG okuva ku kubula oba okukeberebwa ku kuweza emirundi ena mu ddaala ly'okuwona okusinga mu ddaala ery'amangu.
Tusobola okukitegeera nti okwekebejja PCR mu kiseera ekituufu ku nucleic acid mu musaayi oba mu nnyindo z'okufuuyira kweyongedde mu kitundu eky'okubiri n'eky'okusatu (nga January 18 ne 22, 2020).
Okukebera obwerwadde mu musaayi kwongeddwako mu kitundu ekyokuna n'ekyokutaano (nga 27 January 2020 ne 8 February 2020), era obukakafu obwa serology bwongeddwako mu kitundu eky'omusanvu.
Enkyukakyuka zino zisinziira ku kunoonyereza okukoleddwa okunoonya ekiwundu ekisingayo obulungi eky'okunoonyereza ku nucleic acid mu bwangu n'ebiraamo by'omu nnyindo ez'omukka omuli n'obubonero bw'omusaayi, ekyongeddewo obwetaavu bw'ebiraamo eby'enjawulo era ne kiyamba okuleeta obubonero obw'obulabe obw'enjawulo mu bujulizi.
Ate era, waliwo obukakafu obweyongera okutukubiriza okufaayo ku balwadde abalina obubonero n'abataalina bubonero.
N'olwekyo, Zhou et al. flow chart erina okukyusibwa kubanga esonga omuntu atalina bubonero bwa ddwaaliro ng'alina "akabi akatono".
Enkola y'ebitiibwa era yeetaaga okukakasibwa mu kunoonyereza n'ebikolwa ebirala.
Okukomekkereza, tulindirira obujulizi obusingawo era tusaba abasomi baffe okuteekawo endowooza zaabwe.
Okukebera 'omulwadde' ne 'omulwadde' tukukubiriza okukebera n'okugoberera obulagirizi obwaggula mu nsi gy'ova.
