Bangladesh erangirira okufa kwa COVID-19 okuggya mu bantu bataano, omuwendo ogusingawo buli lunaku
Eggulo, Bangladesh yakakasa okufa kwa bantu abalala bataano olw'ekirwadde kya COVID-19 olunaku olwo.
Eno y'omuwendo gw'abantu abasinga okufa mu lunaku olw'akawuka.
Olwaleero, ekitongole kya Bangladesh Institute of Epidemiology, Disease Control and Research (IEDCR) kyabadde kitegeeza nti omuwendo gw'abamaze okukakasibwa nga bali mu ddwaliro mwe muli 114 abakyali mu ddwaliro era 33 be bawonye nga bali waka.
