Amaduuka mu Australia gakendeeza ku bbeeyi y'empapula z'ekyama
Ku Lwomukaaga n'olunnaku olw'eggulo, Woolworths ne Coles, amaduuka ga Australia, gaasembaawo amateeka agafuga okugula ebitabo by'ekyama, nga gawera ebitabo bibiri n'ekitabo kimu buli kintu mu maduuka gonna mu nsi.
Ku Bbalaza, ALDI nayo yatandikawo ekibanja ky'ekika kimu.
Enkyukakyuka zino zaategeezebwa mu bubaka obuli ku mikutu gya Facebook.
Olw'okutya COVID-19, abaguze baali bateeberezebwa okuba nga beeterekera embeera eyinza okubaleetera okwekalakaasa.
