Ebisawo bya laabula ya coronavirus respiratory disease 2019 (COVID-19) ne SARS-CoV-2 ey'ekika kimu birimu enkola ezirabira okubeerawo kwa virus n'ezo ezirabira obutwa obwekika ekirwanyisa obulwadde.
Obulamu bw'akawuka mu bigezo bukakasibwa RT-PCR, ekinoonyereza ku RNA ya coronavirus.
Ekigezo kino kya njawulo era kyakolebwa okunoonya SARS-CoV-2 RNA yokka.
Kikozesebwa okukakasa obulwadde obupya ennyo oba obw'amaanyi.
Okuzuula obutoffaali (serology) kusobola okukozesebwa mu kulongoosa n'okukebera abantu.
Okugezesa obutoffaali kulaga abantu bangi abafunye obulwadde, omuli n'abo abalina obubonero obutono ennyo okubutegeeza oba abataalina bubonero.
Obukakafu obutuufu ku bulwadde n'obutebenkevu bw'ekika mu bantu busobola okuzuulibwa okuva mu biva mu kukebera kuno.
Olw'okugezesebwa okukaluba, nga March 2020 tewali ggwanga lyali liriko bye liyinza kwesiga ku bulwadde mu bantu.
Nga Maaki 23, tewali ggwanga lyalina kugezesa kusukka 3% by'abantu baalyo, era waliwo enjawulo mu bungi bw'okugezesa mu nsi.
Enjawulo eno eyinza okukwata nnyo ku muwendo gw'abafa mu bantu abazuuliddwa, era mu nsi ezimu bayinza okugaanyi nnyo.
Nga bakozesa polymerase chain reaction with real time reverse transcription (rRT-PCR), ekigezo kiyinza okukolebwa ku bifaananyi by'omukka ebiggibwa mu ngeri ezitali zimu, omuli okussa mu nnyindo oba okuyonja.
Ebyava mu kunoonyereza biyinza okulabika mu ssaawa ntono oba mu nnaku bbiri.
RT-PCR ekikoleddwa nga kyekebeddwa mu bulongo esobola okwesiga ekiro ekisooka kyokka nga mulwadde.
Oluvannyuma, akawuka kano kayinza okubula mu nnyindo nga kakyabeera mu biwundu.
Eri abantu abalina akawuka akaakaggwa mu wiiki ey'okubiri, ng'ekirala, ebintu ebiba biweereddwa ebifaananyi biyinza okuggibwa mu nsibuko y'omukka nga bikozesebwa kateter ey'okunywa oba ebintu ebiggibwa mu by'okusuula ebifaananyi biyinza okukozesebwa.
Ekimu ku bigezo bya PCR ebyasoose okukolebwa mu CharitÃ©, Berlin, mu January 2020 nga kikozesa polymerase chain reaction with real-time reverse transcription (rRT-PCR), era kye kiviirako ebikozesebwa 250,000 okugabanyizibwa ekitongole ky'obulamu mu nsi yonna (WHO).
Bungereza nayo yatandika okugezesa nga January 23, 2020. Kkampuni y'omu South Korea eyitibwa Kogenebiotech yatandikawo ekika ky'obusawo, ekipapula ekikebera SARS-CoV-2 ekyesigamiziddwa ku PCR (PowerCheck Coronavirus) nga January 28, 2020.
Enoonya gene "E" eyagabanyiziddwa beta coronavirus zonna, n'erinnya RdRp erikwata ku SARS-CoV-2. Mu China, BGI Group y'emu ku kampuni ezasooka okufuna ekiragiro ky'okukozesa mu bwangu okuva mu China National Medical Products Administration (NMA) ku SARS-CoV-2 ey'ekikonde ekikwatagana ne PCR. Mu Amerika, ekitongole ekivunaanyizibwa ku kujanjaba endwadde (CDC) kigaba RT-PCR ey'omulembe mu kiseera ekituufu mu nkola ya Coronavirus (2019-nCoV) eri ebifo eby'obujjanjabi mu ggwanga.
Ekimu ku bigezo bisatu eby'obutoffaali mu bifaananyi eby'edda eby'ebikozesebwa byavaamu okugezesa okutaliimu kalungi olw'obutaba na bibala mu kugezesa mu CDC mu Atlanta; kino kyavaamu abantu abatannatuuka mu 100 buli lunaku nga beeyisa bulungi mu mwezi gwonna ogw'omwezi gwa Febwali 2020.
Ebigezo ebikozesa ebibinja bibiri tebyali bya bwesige okutuusa nga 28 Febwali 2020, era oluvannyuma laabu za disitulikiti n'eza ssaza zaakkirizibwa okutandika okugezesa.
Ekigezo kino kiweebwa olukusa lwa Food and Drug Administration wansi w'obuyinza obw'ebbeeyi.
Nga March 5, 2020, LabCorp yalangirira okufunibwa kw'ebikebero bya RT-PCR ebya COVID-19 mu ggwanga lyonna.
Quest Diagnostics era yaleetedde okugezesa COVID-19 okulabika mu ggwanga lyonna okuva nga March 9, 2020.
Tewali kikangabwa ku bungi; okutwala n'okukolera ku bifaananyi birina kukolebwa nga bwe kisaanira mu CDC.
Mu Russia, ekigezo kya COVID-19 kyatandikibwawo era ne kifulumizibwa ekitongole kya State Research Center of Virology and Biotechnology, VECTOR.
Nga February 11, 2020, ekigezo kyawandiisibwa ekitongole kya Federal Health Surveillance Service. Nga March 12, 2020, Mayo Clinic yagamba nti yakulaakulanya ekigezo ekikebera obulwadde bwa COVID-19. Nga March 13, 2020, Roche Diagnostics yafuna akkiriza okuva mu FDA ku kikebero ekiyinza okukolebwa mu ssaawa 3.5 ku kigero ekinene, nga kino kisobozesa ekyuma okukebera abantu nga 4,128 mu ssaawa 24.
