Okunoonyereza okwegeraageranya PCR ne CT mu Wuhan mu kifo ekikulu ekirimu ekirwadde kino, kwalaga nti CT ya maanyi okusinga PCR, wadde nga si nnungi nnyo, ng'ebitundu bingi eby'okukuba ebifaananyi bikwatagana n'obulwadde bw'ensusu n'obulwadde obulala.
Okuva mu March 2020, American College of Radiology yalagira nti "TC terina kukozesebwa mu kukebera oba ng'okugezesa okw'olubereberye okuzuula COVID-19".[5] Okuva mu March 2020, CDC yalagira PCR okugezesebwa mu kusooka.
