Angiotensin type 2 enzyme (ECA2) enzyme ekwatagana n'ebweru w'ensiri (enku ze z'ensiri) ez'omu bwongo, mu mpumpo, mu mirambo, mu mutima, mu nsusu, ne mu mazzi.
ECA2 ekendeeza ku nkola ya enzyme eya angiotensin converting enzyme (ECA) ng'ekendeeza ku bungi bwa angiotensin II era ng'eyongeza Ang (1-7), nga kino kifuula eddagala erisuubizo erya kujjanjaba obulwadde bw'omutima.
Ensiimu ey'omuntu eyitibwa hECA2.
Enzamu ey'ekika 2 ey'okuvvuunula angiotensin, enzamu erimu zinc esangibwa ku nsibuko y'ebisenge n'ebitundu ebirala eby'omubiri.
Protein ECA2 erina ekitundu kya peptidase M2 ekya N-terminal ne C-terminal ekitundu eky'amino acid ne colectrin mu kidda.
ECA2 ye protini ya type 1 eya mulundi gumu, era erina ekitundu ekikolera ku buyambi mu nkola ya enzyme ekisangibwa ku nsibuko z'ebitundu by'omubiri mu busawa ne mu bitundu ebirala.
Ekitundu kya ECA2 ekitali kya mu butoffaali kifuluma mu kitundu kya transmembrane nga kifunibwa enziimu endala eyitibwa sheddase, era ekirungo kino ekyefunibwa kifuluma mu musaayi ne kifuluma mu musaayi.
ECA2 eri mu bitundu bingi: ECA2 ekwatiddwa ku lumbe lw'ensiri mu bitundu ebikulu eby'omu bwongo eby'omu bwongo eby'ekika II, enterocyte mu bulago obutonotono, endothelial cells mu mpisa ne mu mazzi, ne mu mubiri gw'ensiri mu bitundu ebisinga obungi.
Ekika kya ECA2 kya mRNA era kisangibwa mu bwongo, mu mubiri oguliko obuzito, mu hypotalamus, ne mu bwongo.
Ekigendererwa ekikulu ekya ECA2 kwe kuba nga kye kiviirako ECA.
ECA ekwata angiotensin ya type I mu angiotensin ya type II ne kiviirako okussa.
ECA2 erina okwekebera phenylalanine okuva mu carboxyminal amino acid okuva mu angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) era n'eyonoona mu angiotensin ey'okusaasaanya emibiri (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-Gist-Pro-OH).
ECA2 era essaawo ebika by'ebika ebirala nga [des-Arg9]-bradicinine, apilin, neurotensin, dinorphine A, ne ghrelin.
ECA2 era erongoosa entambula y'omutambuza wa amino acid eyeewummulamu SLC6A19 era ebadde ekwatagana n'obulwadde bwa Hartnup.
Ng'obutebenkevu bwa transmembrane, ECA2 ekola ng'ekifo ekikulu eky'okuyingira mu buwuka bwa coronaviruses ezimu, omuli HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virus etera SARS); ne SARS-CoV-2 (virus etera COVID-19).
Okusingira ddala, okussa protein ya SARS-CoV ne SARS-CoV2 ey'omugavu S1 ku ekitundu kya ECA2 eky'omu butonde ku mutendera gw'ensiri kivaamu endocytosis n'okuzzaawo akawuka ne enzyme mu endosomes eziri munda mu butonde.
Enkola eno ey'okuyingira era erina okuteekateeka protein S nga ekitundu ky'omusujja ekikwatagana ne serine-protease TMPRSS2, ekirwadde kino ekirimu ekirwadde ekikwatagana n'obulabe bw'abantu.
Kyokka, ebibiina by'abasawo n'ebibiina ebirongoosa biwanukudde okutambulira ku mutindo gw'okuziyiza ECA ne ARB.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu ngeri entegeke obulungi n'okunoonyereza okwakolebwa ku 11 Jjulaayi 2012 kwazuula nti "okukozesa abaziyiza ba ACE kwaliko akakwate n'okukendeeza okw'ebitundu 34% mu bulabe bw'obulwadde bw'ensusu bw'obeera ng'obeera n'abaziyiza".
Ate era, " akabi k'obulwadde bw'ensusu nako kaaliko omuwendo omutono mu balwadde abajjanjabibwa aba ACE inhibitors abaali mu kabi k'obulwadde bw'ensusu, naddala abo abaalina obulwadde bw'omusaayi n'obulwadde bw'omutima.
Okukozesa abaziyiza ba ACE nakyo kyakolebwa okukendeeza okufa okw'olukonvuba, wadde nga ebyavaamu byali bitono nnyo okusinga ku bulwadde bwa kolona".
Ekirwadde kya ECA2 eky'omubiri (rhACE2) kisuubirwa okuba eddagala eriggya mu bulwadde bw'amabeere obw'amaanyi era kirabika nga kyongera ku ddembe ly'omubiri n'obutebenkevu bwa oxygen mu ngulube ezirina obulwadde bw'obutafu bwa mmirimu obuleetebwa obuwuka obuyitibwa lipopolysaccharide.
Ekiseera eky'obulamu bwa rhACE2 mu bantu kiri kumpi essaawa 10 era okutandika kw'omugaso kubaawo eddakiika 30 oluvannyuma lw'ekiseera eky'obudde eky'ebiseera eby'obudde (ekiseera) eby'essaawa 24.
Ebivudde mu kunoonyereza bingi biraga nti rhACE2 eyinza okuba eddagala eriraga obukakafu eri abo abatagumiikiriza obuwuka obuyitibwa classical renin-angiotensin system inhibitors (RAS inhibitors) oba abalwadde abalina angiotensin II ey'omu mubiri.
COVID-19 apps ze zimu ku mpapula z'amasimu ezikozesebwa mu kulabirira abantu nga balwanyisa akawuka ka coronavirus aka 2019-2020, kwe kugamba, okukakasa abantu ("abaagala") abayinza okuba nga baakakwatagana n'abantu abalina akawuka kano.
