Okuva nga April 14, 2020, app eno yali esuubizibwa mu Google Play Store ne Apple App Store.
Nga 12 April, gavumenti yalagula nti enkola y'okukebera abantu yali mu kutendekebwa okw'amaanyi era nti yandibaddewo mu bbanga lya wiiki ntono. Enkola y'emu etegekeddwa mu Ireland ne mu Bufalansa ("StopCovid").
Australia ne New Zealand ziteekateeka apps ezesigamiziddwa ku TraceTogether app eya Singapore ne BlueTrace protocol. Russia eteekateeka okuteekawo geofencing app eri abalwadde abazuuliddwa nga balina COVID-19 ababeera mu Moscow, nga kigendereddwamu okukakasa nti tebasobola kuva waka.
