Omuwendo omungi ogw'abakozi b'ebyobulamu, naddala abajjanjabi, bakazi, era be basinga okuba nga balina akawuka kano.
World Health Organization yalangirira nga February 11, 2020 nti erinnya ly'ekirwadde lino lya "COVID-19".
Akulira ekitongole ky'obulamu mu nsi yonna Tedros Adhanon Ghebreyesus yannyonnyola nti "CO" kitegeeza "corona", "VI" kitegeeza "virusi", "D" kitegeeza bulwadde ate "19" kitegeeza ekirwadde bwe kyazuulibwa nga December 31, 2019.
Erinnya lyalondeddwa okwewala okutegeeza ekifo ekimu (eg: China), ekika ky'ensolo oba ekibinja ky'abantu, okusinziira ku biragiro by'ensi yonna eby'enkola y'amannya okutangira okuvumibwa. Akawuka akaviirako COVID-19 kayitibwa siriimu ey'ekikangabwa eky'omutawaana 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
WHO era ekozesa "akawuka ka COVID-19" ne "akawuka akavudde ku COVID-19" mu bubaka eri abantu.
Obulwadde n'akawuka byombi biyitibwa "coronavirus".
Mu kiseera eky'okusookera ddala mu Wuhan, China, akawuka n'obulwadde byali biyitibwa "coronavirus" ne "Wuhan coronavirus".
Mu January 2020, WHO yasalawo "2019-nCov" ne " 2019-nCoV acute respiratory disease" ng'amannya ag'ekiseera g'akawuka n'obulwadde, okusinziira ku bulagirizi obwa 2015 obukwata ku kukozesa ebifo mu mannya g'obulwadde n'obulwadde.
Amannya ga COVID-19 ne SARS-CoV-2 gaafulumizibwa nga February 11, 2020.
