Mu March, ekitongole ky'obulamu mu nsi yonna (WHO) kyatandika 'SOLIDARITY Trial' okukebera engeri eddagala eririmu ebitundu bina eby'omulwadde gw'obutafuna siriimu gye lisobola okukwata ku bulwadde buno.
Tewali ddagala ly'okulwanyisa eryaliwo, naye ebitongole ebyenjawulo birina kye bikola mu kutandikawo eddagala eryagala okulwanyisa.
Emirimu egy'edda ku SARS-CoV gikolwako kubanga SARS-CoV ne SARS-CoV-2 byombi bikozesa ACE2 okuyingira mu buwuka bw'omuntu.
Waliwo enkola ssatu ez'okulwanyisa ezinoonyerezebwa.
Okusooka, abanoonyereza baagala okukola eddagala eririmu akawuka kano.
Okukozesa akawuka kano, ka kabe nga kabulako oba nga kafudde, kigendereddwamu okuleetawo okwanukula kw'omubiri gw'omuntu okw'amangu ku bulwadde obupya obw'akawuka ka COVID-19.
Enkola ey'okubiri, obulwadde bw'ekika, erina ekigendererwa eky'okuzimba obulwadde obunaakugira obulwadde obw'ekika ekyo okukwata ku bitundu ebimu eby'akawuka.
Mu mbeera ya SARS-CoV-2, okunoonyereza kuno kwesigamye ku puloteni ey'omu nsiko eyamba akawuka okuyingira mu ACE2 enzyme receptor.
Enkola ey'okusatu y'eddagala eririna nucleic acid (eddagala eririna DNA oba RNA, enkola empya ey'okuzimba eddagala).
Enteekateeka z'okugezaako okuziyiza ekirwadde kino ziteekwa okuba nga zaali zikebeddwa ku ngeri gye zikosaamu n'engeri gye zikosaamu. Nga Maaki 16, 2020, ekirwadde ekisooka eky'okugezesa ekirwadde kino kyatandika n'abantu bana mu Seattle.
Akalwadde kano kalimu obutoffaali bw'ekika bw'ekika obutasobola kukosa muntu yenna obwakoppebwa okuva ku kawuka akaviirako obulwadde. Okweyongerayongera kw'ebirwadde ebikugira ebirwadde bya SARS-CoV-2 kwalagibwa ng'ekikangabwa ekirala ekirimu okuteekateeka ekirwadde kino.
Waliwo okugezesebwa okw'ekisawo okusukka mu 300 okwabaddewo okuva mu April 2020.
Okugezesebwa musanvu kwagezaako okugezesa eddagala erikkirizibwa okulwanyisa omusujja gw'ensiri, nga muno mwe muli n'okunoonyereza okuna ku hydroxychloroquine oba chloroquine.
Okukyusa eddagala erirwanyisa akawuka kano kye kisinga mu kunoonyereza mu China, nga waliwo ebigezo bya mirimu 9 mu kitundu kya 3 ekya remdesivir mu mawanga ag'enjawulo okusinziira ku lipoota eyafulumizibwa mu nkomerero ya April.
Okunoonyereza ku by'obujjanjabi ku ddagala n'eddagala ebirwanirira COVID-19 kwabaddewo mu April 2020. Eddagala erimu erirwanyisa akawuka ka siriimu erigenda okukozesebwa mu kujjanjaba COVID-19, omuli remdesivir, chloroquine ne hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir, ne lopinavir/ritonavir nga zikozesebwa wamu ne interferon beta.
Waliwo okugezaako okukakasa nti eddagala erya remdesivir ligenda kulabikira okuva mu March wa 2020.
Obulungi bw'omulwadde bwalabikira mu kulwanyisa remdesivir ng'omusaasizi.
Okukebera mu kitundu III kubadde mu Amerika, China ne Italy. Chloroquine, ekikozesebwa edda okujjanjaba omusujja, yakeberebwa mu China mu February 2020 nga kirina ebivudde mu kusooka.
Kyokka, waliwo okusaba okw'okukebera okunoonyereza.
