Kyokka, ekitongole kya Wuhan Institute of Virology, wadde nga kikubiriza eddagala lya gramu emu buli lunaku, kyalabula nti emirundi ebiri ku ddwaaliro eryo lya kabi nnyo era lisobola okutaataaganya obulamu bw'omuntu.
Nga 28 March 2020, FDA yafulumya ekiragiro ekikwata ku kukozesa mu bwangu hydroxychloroquine ne chloroquine nga bwe kisaanira ku basawo abalwanyisa COVID-19. Enkyusa ey'omusanvu ey'ebiragiro bya China era birimu interferon, ribavirin oba umifenovir ezikozesebwa okulwanyisa COVID-19.
Ebisooka biraga nti eddagala eddene ery'ekika kya ribavirin lyetaagisa okuziyiza SARS-CoV-2 mu in vitro.
Nitazoxanid yasalibwa okwongera okuyigirizibwa mu bulamu oluvannyuma lw'okulaga nti SARS-CoV-2 tewalimu buzibu bwa maanyi.Okwekenneenya kwalaga nti protein ey'ekika ky'omuzira eyasooka mu kuteekateeka kwa serine transmembrane protease 2 (TMPRSS2) y'esinga obukulu mu kuyingira SARS-CoV-2 okuyita mu kuyingira mu ACE2.
Okukebera ku chlorokini ne hydroxychloroquine nga ziriko ne azithromycin, birina obunafu bungi nnyo ebiremesezza abasawo okutandika okukozesa eddagala lino nga tebanakebera nnyo. Oseltamivir teremesa SARS-CoV-2 mu vitro era terina mugaso gwonna mu kujjanjaba COVID-19.
Obudde bw'ebirungo (cytokine storm) buyinza okuba obuzibu mu biseera eby'oluvannyuma ebya COVID-19 ey'amaanyi.
Waliwo obujulizi nti hydroxychloroquine esobola okuba n'obutebenkevu bwa cytokine. Tocilzumab yateekebwa mu biragiro by'obujjanjabi mu National Health Commission of China oluvannyuma lw'okumaliriza okunoonyereza okutono.
Okugezesebwa okw'ekitundu 2 okutasengekeddwa mu butonde bwonna mu Italy kugenda mu maaso oluvannyuma lw'okulaga nti abantu abalina obulwadde obw'amaanyi balwadde.
Bwe guba gwakolebwa wamu n'okwekebejjebwa omusaayi gwa serum ferritin okunoonyereza ku cytocin storms, gujja kusobola okuziyiza embeera eno, era nga kino kye kigambibwa nti kye kiviiriddeko abantu abamu okufiira mu bulwadde obwo.
Interleukin-6 receptor antagonist yakkirizibwa FDA okusinziira ku kunoonyereza ku nsonga ez'edda ku kujjanjaba Steroid Refractory Cytokine Release Syndrome eyakolebwa mu ngeri endala, CAR T cell therapy mu 2017.
Okutuusa kati, tewali bujulizi bwa kugenga n'okukebera nti tocilzumab y'ekikyasinze okujjanjaba SRS.
